    <description><![CDATA[
# DesktopPet — AI Desktop Pet for Windows

A cute AI desktop pet that lives on your desktop. Chat with AI, analyze documents, search the web — all from a floating companion.

## Features
- **Multi-theme** — Orange Cat, Yellow Baby, Ultramarines Warrior, Claude theme
- **Multi-model AI** — DeepSeek, OpenAI (ChatGPT), and custom model providers
- **Streaming responses** — Real-time AI replies like ChatGPT
- **Document analysis** — Import TXT/PDF/DOCX/MD/JSON/CSV files for AI analysis
- **Web search** — Optional Bing search + automatic weather detection
- **Conversation management** — Switch/delete conversations, auto-generated titles
- **Auto-update** — Checks GitHub Releases on startup, one-click download & install
- **Local storage** — API keys and chat history stored locally, never uploaded
    ]]></description>
    <summary>AI desktop pet — chat, analyze documents, search the web from a cute floating companion</summary>
